@NODE Main "Users guide for GIFComposer version 0.10 beta"

         Welcome to GIFComposer, the GIF-animation creator
                      made by Tomas ≈kesson

      This is a beta  version of  GIFComposer,  the Muified
      animation-creator. The reason why it is called "beta"
      is  that  the  program is not fully finished yet as I
      need to include more features,  but  it is usable and
      do not include any bugs (I hope).

      Please read this documentation through, or if you are
      impatient and want to try GIFComposer directly, do it,
      because it's not that hard to use.


